headline: Cadence Unveils AI-Driven ROCS X AI-Enabled Molecular Search, Unlocking Multi-trillion Molecule Virtual Screening
summary: BOSTON, September 25, 2025--Cadence Molecular Sciences announced ROCS X, an AI-enabled virtual screening solution that conducts 3D searches of trillions of drug-like molecules.

headline: Taiwan Semiconductor Unveils Ultra-Advanced Chip Tech
summary: Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Co. (NYSE: TSM) shares were trending on Thursday as the company showcased its new A14, or 1.4nm, logic process technology at its North America Technology Symposium in Santa Clara, California. headline: 2 High-Flying Stocks to Consider Right Now and 1 Facing Headwinds
summary: "You get what you pay for" often applies to expensive stocks with best-in-class business models and execution. While their quality can sometimes justify the premium, they typically experience elevated volatility during market downturns when expectations change.
